## Upstream Sync Policy

Lovon Teams tracks upstream Paperclip for bug fixes and security updates.
The remote `upstream` is configured to `https://github.com/paperclipai/paperclip.git` so that
maintainers can sync selectively. Rebase merges from upstream are welcome; please preserve the
original commit author metadata so the contribution history remains intact.

